  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Park Hotel Gran Bosco is on half board</p>
<p>Enjoy a varied cold buffet breakfast every morning, often including hot options such as eggs and pancakes is on offer. In the evening you will be treated to four courses including a vegetable buffet.</p>
<p>On New Years Eve the hotel puts on a delicious gala dinner. A fun way to welcome in the New Year!</p>]]></cateringDescription>
